Hey, guys.
Hello, babies.

00:37.333 --> 00:38.500
Get in bed, girly.

00:38.500 --> 00:40.633
Hey, good morning,
darlin'.

00:43.167 --> 00:45.167
- No, no.
- Oh, Teiren.

